<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="iddb22af35-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">2006—Par. (1). <ref href="/us/pl/109/351">Pub. L. 109–351</ref> and 109–356 amended par. (1) identically, striking out “and closed banks in the District of Columbia” before semicolon at end.</p>
</note>
